title: REQUEST_PLAYER_COMMERCE_SESSION

0x96F93CCE// RequestPlayerCommerceSession
void REQUEST_PLAYER_COMMERCE_SESSION(char* playerSrc, int skuId);Parameters:playerSrc: The player handleskuId: The ID of the SKU.Requests the specified player to buy the passed SKU. This'll pop up a prompt on the client, which upon acceptance
will open the browser prompting further purchase details.
